<a href="http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/patellar-tendinitis/basics/definition/con-20024441">Patellar tendinitis</a>. Mayo Foundation for Medical Education and Research (accessed 10/03/2016).</li>
	<li>Orthopaedic Trauma Association: <a href="http://orthoinfo.aaos.org/topic.cfm?topic=A00523">Patellar (Kneecap) Fractures</a>. American Academy of Orthopaedic Surgeons (accessed 10/03/2016).</li>
</ul>




